Title: Door to the Ren'dorei
Description:
If this investigation involves the Void, it would be wise to consult the void elves. We must head to Telogrus Rift and report the situation.

I'll speak with Umbric. He'll be able to mobilize the Riftwalkers to our cause.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Speak to Alleria Windrunner in Telogrus Rift.

Objectives.Text: Use the Void Rift to enter Telogrus Rift
